plot: After Dollar-nator breaks up with a video game, he turns to Fanboy & Chum Chum to help him find someone to grow obsolete with.Something weird has happened to Oz. He's selling his collectibles! The boys try to find out where he got the idea.—Anonymous

Fanboy and Chum Chum play cupids when Dollar-nator falls in love with Oz's new robot librarian, Julie Android./The boys find a new pet that's a cross between a rattlesnake, a skunk, and a porcupine. This animal is called the "rattleskunkupine," but Fanboy and Chum Chum name it "Scooter." They have to hide it from Oz when they learn that it's terrorizing the city.
